{"tid":971282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"走飲筒平一蚊會唔會係解決成個環保問題嘅方法","createTime":"2019-01-06T13:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T15:04:36.000Z","uid":215700,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2fc4ff174ed20ef67882fe38cf84b04223788d","tid":971282,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"老老實實 大家都知要解決飲筒問題係無咩可能<br />\n最大可能只係減少對飲筒嘅需求<br />\n平一蚊之後起碼有四分一人唔會要飲筒 <br />\n咁起碼真係舒緩到個問題 唔係好似依家咁個個屌曬鬼<br />\n我知咁即係變相要飲筒就貴一蚊 但我真係諗唔到方法可以唔影響大眾又滿足到班離曬地嘅環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf3c1d954fd869b63421849beefaf3978c2023d","tid":971282,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"膠係石油嘅副產品<br />\n你唔攞嚟整膠咪又係倒落海？<br />\n唔通為咗用少啲膠而泵少啲石油？"},{"pid":"a94ae602680a639ce098a239f3b7a97660fadf81","tid":971282,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"應該政府收膠袋徵費咁"},{"pid":"5e4870aba20d77383768b9cb33970a53426e757f","tid":971282,"uid":129882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"呢啲先叫企業支持環保<br />\n<br />\n平時係企業以環保之名縮減成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果佢真係咁做， 我第一個支持"},{"pid":"a0eaf7c2d00537a101a6a28e84c2da76c0d7d980","tid":971282,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"飲筒加一蚊 好過唔要走一蚊"},{"pid":"df87ad63f4a61aa88ca7c7fbe8f715dc4f18cc77","tid":971282,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本就係  加一蚊 減一蚊又好"},{"pid":"6e2c06339d1dfddd1485f418f5fb2f9585ef928f","tid":971282,"uid":41076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"只會將個餐加返一蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee6c82ba550f9ff9ff9a6d998523ffcf1ba55db","tid":971282,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"根本就係on9，早兩日食飯，一杯凍飲，走飲筒但係用膠匙羹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有鐵匙羹又唔撚用<br />\n<br />\n利申：覺得應該環保，但反環保撚"},{"pid":"d2a480c4b0c624480989fd2dd59dfe605b3cceda","tid":971282,"uid":85556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"飲筒加一蚊都有人撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平十倍買一大袋旁身好過"},{"pid":"c6654b9dd1281f86f26ce3d279ba252be0d4939d","tid":971282,"uid":20634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"賺少咗不了"},{"pid":"6221d552ee5eacd4c8266fdc01ffd45a358d2380","tid":971282,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"唔會, 千奇唔好比人 Spin 左因為錢平貴就可以郁飲筒. 今日平第二日加返你就比佢收貔.<br />\n<br />\n呢 D 係 Sunk Cost 本來就唔應該計, 就好似電費水費租咁. 呢一刻佢走塑下一刻可以用第二 D 理由又減供應或者加價.<br />\n<br />\n走塑 =/= 環保<br />\n<br />\n超級市場膠袋就係好好例子, 佢地一樣用膠袋做其他包裝, 重食埋你膠袋錢. 邊有咁撚戇鳩既事可以出現?"},{"pid":"4195d8dcf7d27b7a4158d096c6b20f1f786df54d","tid":971282,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"研究取代品啦 懶過鬼咁<br />\n唔用飲管 無疑係斬腳趾避沙蟲 飲可樂點唔用飲管呀戇鳩！"},{"pid":"d767a3fe9857b69752fe31d809d039200008652e","tid":971282,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=gourmet&amp;aid=16158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmenclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dgourm